OL,3,CFamily say surgery for 'locked jaw'
OL,4,Cwould transform daughter's life
OL,6,FA family from Lancashire warn time is
OL,7,Frunning out to help their daughter who
OL,8,Fhas a rare condition which means her
OL,9,Fjaw is permanently locked closed.
OL,11,FLauren Bolton, 29, from Rossendale is
OL,12,Fnow living in constant pain and unable
OL,13,Fto eat solid food and her family fear
OL,14,Fher health will continue to
OL,15,Fdeteriorate without urgent surgery.
OL,17,F"I can't imagine a life not in pain,
OL,18,Fbecause I have lived in pain for so
OL,19,Flong".
