OL,3,CFamily say surgery for 'locked jaw'
OL,4,Cwould transform daughter's life
OL,6,FLauren is entirely restricted to a
OL,7,Fliquidised diet and her weight andBMI
OL,8,Fhas dropped to a dangerously low level.
OL,10,FShe said "it even hurts her to talk"
OL,11,Fand she is in "constant pain".
OL,13,FHer mother Denise said: "If that money
OL,14,Fwas available and Lauren was able to
OL,15,Fhave the surgery it would give her so
OL,16,Fmuch to look forward to."
OL,18,F"It is difficult to imagine Lauren
OL,19,Fleading a normal life, she can't go
OL,20,Fout to eat and doesn't socialise now,
OL,21,Fwhich is very difficult."
