OL,3,CFamily say surgery for 'locked jaw'
OL,4,Cwould transform daughter's life
OL,6,FLauren is now just six stone and under
OL,7,Fthe care of a dietician. Her family
OL,8,Fare worried about the impact on her
OL,9,Forgans and fear she could die before
OL,10,Fsurgery.
OL,12,FHer parents have been told there are
OL,13,Fonly a handful of surgeons who can
OL,14,Fcarry out bilateral jaw joint
OL,15,Freplacement surgery and most only work
OL,16,Fin private practice.
OL,18,FThe cost of this surgery is #80,000,
OL,19,Fwith an additional cost of #10,000 for
OL,20,Farthroscopy, using a camera to show
OL,21,Fthe joint space.
