OL,3,CFamily say surgery for 'locked jaw'
OL,4,Cwould transform daughter's life
OL,6,FLauren's parents have set up a with
OL,7,Fthe target of raising #95,000 to start
OL,8,Fthe treatment as soon as possible.
OL,10,FToni Bull, a nurse and health visitor
OL,11,Fknows how difficult it is to live with
OL,12,Fthe painful condition as Lauren's and
OL,13,Fsaid she had no quality of life.
OL,15,FShe was in constant pain and unable to
OL,16,Feat solid food and paid privately for
OL,17,Fthe surgery at Harley Street.
OL,19,FShe said it transformed her life and
OL,20,Fnow she is part of a support group for
OL,21,Fothers diagnosed with jaw conditions.
